data.description: Well maintained Woodbury home shows like new construction!  Built in 2016, this 4 bed 4 bath home has incredible flexibility of spaces.  On the main floor there is a "flex room" which can be used as an office, a study, a reading space or even a formal dining room!  The south facing back of the home is light filled and has 9' ceilings which give it an even more spacious feel.  The large main floor family room, dining area and kitchen are perfect for entertaining and daily living!  Large maintenance-free deck offers more dining and entertaining space!  There is even a "Planning Center" off the kitchen which can be used as an office, recipe area or even a homework room.  Upstairs there is a MASSIVE game room for just "hanging out" and is the favorite room for all! Also upstairs you find all 4 bedrooms, each with walk-in closet.  Upstairs laundry for convenience.  The walkout basement offers fireplace, tons of space and 4th bath. Invisible fence and irrigation system. Community pool also.
